sp.
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FC67F892BCC5C892" bold="true" box="[966,1008,1919,1940]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">H–J</emphasis>
). 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FBA4F892BB23C892" bold="true" box="[1029,1046,1919,1940]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">A</emphasis>
. Plants producing spermogonia and aecia on the leaf surface in the field. 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FE11F84EBEF5C8BE" bold="true" box="[432,448,1955,1976]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">B</emphasis>
. Aecia on the lower leaf surface. 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FD5FF84FBC3AC8BE" bold="true" box="[766,783,1954,1976]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">C</emphasis>
. Vertical section of a spermogonium. 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FBDBF84EBBBEC8BE" bold="true" box="[1146,1163,1955,1976]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">D</emphasis>
. Vertical section of an aecium surrounded with peridia. 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FED6F82ABEB2C8DA" bold="true" box="[375,391,1991,2012]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">E</emphasis>
