<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FE22F806BEB9C706" bold="true" box="[387,396,2027,2048]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">I</emphasis>
. Vertical section of a uredinium. 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FD6FF806BDEFC706" bold="true" box="[718,730,2027,2048]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">J</emphasis>
. Vertical section of a telium. Scale bars: 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FBC5F807BBBBC706" bold="true" box="[1124,1166,2026,2048]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">C, J</emphasis>
