<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FF44F7E2BFC1C722" bold="true" box="[229,244,2063,2084]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">F</emphasis>
= 100 μm, 
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFCFFFD9FEC2F7E3BE43C722" bold="true" box="[355,374,2062,2084]" pageId="28" pageNumber="249">G</emphasis>
= 5 μm.
</paragraph>
